"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-american-swimmer-regan-smith-fired-up-for-backstroke-battles-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Regan Smith looking on after the women's 200m butterfly final on Day Six of the 2024 United States Olympic Team Swimming Trials at Lucas Oil Stadium on June 20 in Indianapolis, Indiana.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.5587618425862525e-12, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.577735034342423e-28, \"text\": \"Regan Smith\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9993482898472874, \"rank\": 0.0006453906856619998, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"score\": 0.6265994964938559, \"rank\": 0.549997438964692, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP  Published\\u00c2Jun 23, 2024, 04:25 PM  Updated\\u00c2Jun 23, 2024, 07:50 PM  LOS ANGELES\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093Regan Smith is back and ready for battle at the Paris Olympics, where she thinks a 100m backstroke duel with Australian Kaylee McKeown could produce a historic result.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999679152610474, \"rank\": 3.077214885822289e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith, 22, clocked 57.13 seconds to win the event at the US Olympic swimming trials last week, regaining the world record she first claimed as a 17-year-old in 2019 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 when she also set a 200m back world record.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\", \"score\": 0.5975359342914057, \"rank\": 0.6735395189005082, \"text\": \"US Olympic swimming trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A crisis of confidence and drop in form saw Smith settle for two silver medals and a bronze at the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Olympics, where fellow 22-year-old McKeown won the 100m and 200m backstroke.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9840403915970677e-19, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aussie, who first claimed the 100m back world record in 2021, lowered both the 100m and 200m marks in 2023 and clocked the second-fastest 200m backstroke time ever at the Australian trials in June.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999679152610474, \"rank\": 3.077214885822289e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith, who has been re-energised by working with coach Bob Bowman, former mentor of Olympic superstar Michael Phelps, was thrilled to break out of her backstroke doldrums weeks before an expected meeting with the Australian star on the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s biggest stage.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.8218685855295298, \"rank\": 0.21673793623371407, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowman_Gum\", \"score\": 0.6227448611113158, \"rank\": 0.6057940478945644, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowman_Gum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowman_Gum\"}, {\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961340130219822e-60, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian_Star\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian_Star\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think 56 (seconds) is a possibility, for sure,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith said.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhether it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s me or one of my competitors, who knows.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not going to sell myself short, absolutely not.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Only five women have broken 58 seconds in the 100m back and all of them will be in Paris: Smith, McKeown, Aussie Mollie O\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Callaghan, Canadian Kylie Masse and American Katharine Berkoff, who joined the club with her runner-up finish to Smith at the trials.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.7852430476932757e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999339355549827, \"rank\": 6.58857625292169e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999895055293994, \"rank\": 1.0489654398672257e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1922, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katharine Berkoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if O\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Callaghan opts out of the backstroke to focus on other events, it promises to be a thriller, and Smith expects to be in the thick of it.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat was an amazing race but it wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a perfect race,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said of her record-setting trials final.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI know there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s things that I can clean up and do better, and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to work towards that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Smith, who also won the 200m butterfly and 200m backstroke in Indianapolis to line up a trio of individual events in Paris, said the feeling of her world record swim was \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cso different\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d to her first, five years ago at the world championships.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2436, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9993482898472874, \"rank\": 0.0006453906856619998, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 2491, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.7852430476932757e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhen you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re 17, when you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re a teenager and I had not really done much to my name yet \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it was very easy,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI had no pressure on me.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody really expected much out of me, and so it was so easy to walk into races feeling so fearless and not really caring what the outcome was.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI really just shocked myself at that meet in 2019 because I didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t believe I was capable of it.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now tonight, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m in a much different place in my life.\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a lot older, obviously.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pressure is a lot different.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut I think I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve learnt a lot over these five years, and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve had a lot of lows, in backstroke, in particular.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Smith said she felt it was a mental block that kept her from progressing in the backstroke.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFor a long time, I viewed swimming as like a job, and it was a business trip.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a time and a place for that.\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, I have a job to do, but at the same time this is just fun, and thank God it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a sport.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t life or death.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI just want to lean into the fun side 100 per cent and I think that just makes it a lot easier to go out there and let rip and give your best effort every single time.\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I know Kaylee will.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Meanwhile on June 22, Caeleb Dressel powered to victory in the 100m butterfly at the trials to line up another title defence in Paris, where Katie Ledecky will go for a historic fourth straight 800m freestyle gold.\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 4022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3830, \"end\": 3844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}, {\"begin\": 3936, \"end\": 3941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.7852430476932757e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Said Dressel: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve felt every emotion that I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m capable of.\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tough.\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So really the motto is one stroke at a time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dAFP, REUTERS  Swimming  Olympics 2024  United States  Australia  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4159, \"end\": 4162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999998760072307, \"rank\": 1.239809685781288e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 4164, \"end\": 4171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5856065843450188, \"rank\": 0.7063993248417074, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4213, \"end\": 4222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9956285245820453, \"rank\": 0.004320674587347109, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 4256, \"end\": 4264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": []}]}"